### Orions Belte

Norwegian trio from Oslo. Key confirmed details:
- Genre: Neo-psych pop, downtempo, "somewhere between 60s surf band, easy-listening library music, Saint Etienne, and Air"
- Guitarist Oyvind Blomstrom: uses Bigsby vibrato as a primary expressive tool (not just tuning aid — active pitch wobble mid-phrase)
